The paper deals with machine learning models for click prediction in search advertisement, which falls under the categories of information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of regularization techniques (cs.LG) and the impact of delays in updating models (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper includes experiments with image-based click prediction (cs.CV). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.AI, and cs.CV.
